summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of Lots 1 and 2, Block 1, Maynard's Addition to Georgetown; Lots 5 to 9 inclusive, Block 3, Central Park Addition; Lots 1 to 5 inclusive and the south 10 feet of Lot 6, Blocks 33 and 34, Boulevard Place Addition; and Lots 5 and 6, Block 17, Wood's Supplemental Plat of Blocks 16 and 17, Burke's 2nd Addition; with respect to Use and Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended by adding thereto two new sections numbered 2-273 and 17-220, respectively.
